
This directory contains unit tests. 

CREATE TEST
-----------
To create a new unit test you need to
 1) create a test either by copying and modifying `file_test.cpp.template` or creating a new cpp file from scratch.
 2) add the file as a program to build in `generate_makefile.sh`. DO NOT MODIFY any of the `Makefile/.am/.in` directly!!!
 3) Run `sh generate_makefile.sh` to generate proper `Makefile.am` and reconfigure project to generate `Makefile.in` and `Makefile`.

RUN TESTS
---------
Type `make check` in this directory or one of the parent directories.
